        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Congressional Voting Accountability Act</b></p> <p>This resolution amends the Rules of the House of Representatives to eliminate proxy voting and remote committee activity, to require a recorded vote for any question put before the House, and to require affirmative or negative votes for record votes in the House.</p> <p>The resolution also requires the Chair to entertain a point of order that a quorum is not present during general debate.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
